{"tid":2440667,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》召喚寫信師 為手足送暖","createTime":"2021-03-10T06:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T15:02:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9569fb3f7af722f5cecf56ba2d37d943dab1bd3a","tid":2440667,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/YX6VCJL7L5ADVFGSHATK7F4OC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FYX6VCJL7L5ADVFGSHATK7F4OC4%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwpldAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=fbf30f23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FYX6VCJL7L5ADVFGSHATK7F4OC4%2F&h=81b47050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/YX6VCJL7L5ADVFGSHATK7F4OC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》召喚寫信師 為手足送暖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EnTFB4OVxMbs4xp4NmsTK6b9S_w=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LZ5LOX3J6BCPZA4EIBRZF5HG4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEnTFB4OVxMbs4xp4NmsTK6b9S_w%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLZ5LOX3J6BCPZA4EIBRZF5HG4A.jpg&h=c94f9bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄒家成（左）和李嘉達（右）現還柙赤柱監獄。<br />\n<br />\n暴政將一場民主派初選定性「顛覆國家政權」，以國安法之名將43人推入囚室，自由無期。誠如黃之鋒親筆信所言，在牢房中跟恐懼及孤寂搏鬥絕不容易，尤其部份人被單獨囚禁，與人溝通的權利亦被剝奪。不少香港人化身「寫信師」，希望一份微小支持，超越高牆穿透鐵窗，溫暖每一位在囚者。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：岑敖暉期待探訪 慢必獄中唱歌<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》冀能成為連接高牆內外的窗口，誠邀讀者執筆寫信，向200名在囚手足送上你們的支持，我們挑選後每日在報章刊登，讓失去自由的手足看到你們的心意，累積力量撐下去。（讀者電郵請發送到 letterstoprison@appledaily.com）"},{"pid":"43b4fd176dbe7067a03b0127f9673fbc7ca48654","tid":2440667,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T06:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid